      <p>
        You are currently logged in as <em><xsl:value-of select="/clam/@user" /></em>. Make sure to <strong><a href="{/clam/@baseurl}/logout/?oauth_access_token={/clam/@oauth_access_token}">log out</a></strong> when you are done.
